        <p>Please log in with your credentials to kick-start the onboarding process.</p>

        <div style="margin: 30px 0; text-align: center;">
          <a href="<%= loginUrl || '#' %>" style="background-color: #4a90e2; color: white; padding: 12px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold;">
            Login Now
          </a>
        </div>

